data.description: Beautiful, spacious unit in CitySide. This 3 bedroom, 2-1/2 bath, two-story townhouse features a large floorpan, one car garage, upgraded kitchen cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. Situated perfectly just off 95, this gated community is only minutes from the heart of Downtown West Palm, Whole Foods, Palm Beach Outlets, PBI Airport, Rosemary Square, the beach and more! CitySide boasts a resort style pool, newly updated fitness center, running trail and 24 hour security.
